data.description: Prospective investors and prospective first-time homebuyers, take a look at this charming 4-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom residence available for purchase in North Charleston, SC. Situated just a 15-minute drive from downtown Charleston, this property offers convenient access to the city center. It's also conveniently located just 10 minutes away from Park Circle and the airport. The promising growth in this area suggests a potential increase in property value over the upcoming years. Additionally, the house boasts a fully fenced backyard, ideal for dog owners. The property is meticulously maintained, and it's currently tenant-occupied.
